df$Positivity_factor <- factor(df$Positivity, levels = 1:9)
df$Participant_factor <- as.factor(df$Participant)

fit <- ordinal::clmm(Positivity_factor ~ mean_pedcounts + (1|Participant_factor), data =  df)
